<section style="padding-top: 120px; max-width: 900px;">
  <div class="feature-card" style="padding: 60px 50px;">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      <span class="section-tag">Privacy</span>
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: April 29, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="markdown-body">
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>Vermeil only collects the minimum amount of data required to function. This includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Guild IDs and User IDs for configuration storage.</li>
        <li>Message content (only when necessary for specific features like AutoMod).</li>
        <li>Voice channel data for VoiceMaster features.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Data</h2>
      <p>Data is used exclusively to provide the bot's services. We do not sell or share any user data with third parties.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Data is stored until the bot is removed from the server or a manual deletion request is made via our support server.</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; border: 1px dashed var(--accent-glow); border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Questions? Join our <a href="<%= config.supportServer %>" style="font-weight: 700;">Support Server</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
